data.description: Seller will contribute $10K toward a 2-1 buydown or other closing costs!!! Charming centrally located Beaverton Ranch home on a large lot in a quiet neighborhood.  Three bedrooms and two baths with both a living room and family room.  Efficient multi-split AC/heater system, updated kitchen, vinyl windows, and a newer roof installed in 2015.  Hardwood floors in the bedrooms and vinyl flooring in the kitchen and family room.  Roomy backyard with a covered deck.  Super convenient location:  close to highways, Nike, and shopping.  Tons of potential here to make this your very own!!
